item.title: Vivo Y73 Released at Rs.20990 in India
item.description: Vivo has launched their latest 4G Smartphone in India ‘Vivo Y73’. The device comes with MediaTek Helio G95. Vivo Y73 priced at 20990 in India. It comes with only one variant right now that is 8GB RAM and 128 GB storage, and expandable memory up to 1TB.
item.author: team gagetin

item.title: OnePlus has launched their lowest range 5G phone in India, OnePlus Nord CE 5G
item.description: OnePlus Nord CE 5G comes with 64MP triple camera and 16 MP selfie camera, both front and rear camera features portrait mode and the refresh rate of display 90Hz.
item.author: team gagetin
